                        "name": "Two Actions"
                    },
                    "frequency": "once per day",
                    "effect": "You draw a seed and cast it into a space within 30 feet. A small tree sprouts within 10 minutes, producing 5 fruits. A creature who eats the fruit with an Interact action regains 1d6+2 Hit Points and receives as much nourishment as one meal for a typical human. After an hour, the tree and all its fruits wither away.",
